of concern

21:33.691 --> 21:35.559
For scooter the turtle.

21:35.560 --> 21:40.063
We were both overwhelmed
by the amount of cards
and flowers that you all sent.

21:40.064 --> 21:42.999
Unfortunately, because of
scooter's sugar allergies,

21:43.000 --> 21:45.836
He was not allowed to eat
the chocolate that you sent.

21:45.837 --> 21:49.673
Bet that didn't stop you
and your mom from scarfing
all that stuff down.

21:51.409 --> 21:54.144
Ladies and gentlemen,
let's have a warm welcome back

21:54.145 --> 21:57.581
For scooter -
the fully recovered turtle!

22:00.752 --> 22:04.254
Scooter! Scooter!

22:04.255 --> 22:05.822
Ah!

22:05.823 --> 22:08.392
